<div class='commentinfo comment_warning'>
2010-04-24 11:36:54 (1498 days ago)
<div id='contact-151743'>fleurvert5 (151743)</div> </div>
<div class='commentbox'>
This is a beginner section. The water is not very dangerous. As a river guide, I have taken 6<br/>
year-olds down this section and they have fared just fine. I don't want anyone to think that they<br/>
can't do this section from being scared. After reading your water, you should just stay away from a<br/>
hole that looks bigger than your skill level and enjoy a perfect scenic float trip! </div>
</td>
</tr>
